:"FAQPage","mainEntity":[[{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      What’s included in the Adobe Creative Cloud Pro plan?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"The Creative Cloud Pro plan has 20+ creative apps and Adobe Firefly creative AI for images, video, and audio. Create with Adobe Photoshop, Illustrator, Premiere, After Effects, InDesign, and Acrobat Pro. Get unlimited access to standard creative AI image and vector features like Text to Image in Firefly and Generative Fill in Photoshop. And get 4,000 credits for premium creative AI video and audio features like Text to Video and Translate Audio. Plus, perks like templates, cloud storage, and thousands of fonts from the Adobe Fonts library are also included.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      What’s the price of the Creative Cloud Pro plan?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Save 50% on the Creative Cloud Pro plan. It’s just Regularly at US$69.99/mo US$34.99/mo for the first 3 months and then US$69.99/mo after that (annual billed monthly). New subscribers only. See terms.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      What’s the difference between buying the Creative Cloud Pro plan and buying a single product plan, like the Single App plan for Photoshop?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"The Creative Cloud Pro plan has more than 20 creative applications, including Photoshop, to grow your creative skillset, plus Adobe Firefly creative AI for images, video, and audio. Single App plans include one Creative Cloud app of your choice and access to basic creative AI. If you’re considering purchasing more than one Single App plan or if you are interested in Firefly creative AI, the Creative Cloud Pro plan is the easiest way to get it all in one subscription at a great price.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      How many devices can I use with Creative Cloud Pro?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Your subscription lets you activate each of the 20+ Creative Cloud apps across desktop, mobile, and web on up to two devices (or virtual machines) at a time, but you may not use the same app on both devices simultaneously.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      Will all the apps in Creative Cloud Pro download at once?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"You control which of the Creative Cloud apps you download, when you download each one, and which devices you install them on.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      What are the system requirements for Creative Cloud Pro?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Adobe partners with hardware and software providers to take advantage of the most up-to-date technologies for mobile devices, desktops, and web browsers. Apps in the Creative Cloud Pro plan work with the latest operating systems for macOS, Windows, iOS, and Android, and two prior versions. View the system requirements.","@type":"Answer"}},{"@type":"Question","name":"\n      Is Adobe Creative Cloud worth the cost?\n    ","acceptedAnswer":{"text":"Yes. The Adobe Creative Cloud membership plan provides more tools, generative AI, cloud features, continuous updates, and added perks and benefits, ideal for creative professionals. See why creative professionals should choose Adobe Creative Cloud Pro.","@type":"Answer"}}]]}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/editorial-card/editorial-card.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/layout.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/popover.bundle.css"><link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="https://prod.adobeccstatic.com/unav/1.5/profile.bundle.css"><link rel="preload" as="script" crossorigin="anonymous" href="/libs/blocks/tabs/tabs.js"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/styles/rounded-corners.css"><link rel="preload" as="script" crossorigin="anonymous" href="/libs/blocks/merch-card/merch-card.js"><link rel="stylesheet" href="/libs/blocks/merch-card/merch-card.css"><